OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,6,Fand bright on Saturday. Mostly dry
OL,7,Fwith variable cloud and bright spells
OL,8,Fon Sunday and Monday, but a chance of
OL,9,Fthe odd spell of rain.
